Admin Access Route:
- /adminpanel0109tpa2026

Admin Functional Areas:
- login
- session restore / logout
- admissions management
- records export
- results CRUD
- announcements CRUD
- faculty CRUD
- settings save/load
- analytics / insights
- backup / restore
- activity log


10. Security Features

- Session-based admin authentication
- Custom admin panel path
- Admin remember-cookie support
- Default-credential protection logic
- Input validation on both client and server
- CNIC normalization and validation
- Phone validation
- File size validation
- File type validation
- Secure upload handling
- SQL parameterized queries
- CSRF-style protections for admin actions
- Same-origin checks
- Honeypot anti-bot field in enrollment form
- Rate limiting for sensitive endpoints
- Security headers
- Safer health endpoint behavior


11. File Upload Handling

Student Uploads:
- Passport size picture
- Validation for type and size
- Client-side crop support

Faculty Uploads:
- Photo upload
- Admin crop support

Results Uploads:
- PDF uploads

Upload Folders:
- uploads/student_photos/
- uploads/faculty_photos/
- uploads/gallery_images/
- uploads/results/


12. Downloaded Admission Form

The project includes a formal downloadable admission form:
- available for admin use
- available to students when allowed
- PDF output
- professional academic layout
- student details
- student photograph
- important note
- signature boxes
- single-page optimization

Form File Naming Pattern:
- student_name_roll_no_date.pdf


13. SEO and Indexing Support

Implemented SEO Features:
- meta description
- canonical URL
- robots directives
- Googlebot directives
- Google Search Console verification meta tag support
- Open Graph tags
- Twitter meta tags
- structured data \(JSON-LD\)
- robots.txt
- sitemap index
- page sitemap
- result sitemap
- Railway/free-subdomain compatible indexing setup

Purpose:
- Better indexing
- Better search visibility
- Cleaner social sharing preview


14. Analytics and Insights

Website analytics support includes:
- section/page visit tracking
- live presence tracking
- unique visitor insights
- most-viewed sections
- last 7 days summary
- admin dashboard insights
- live visitor count


15. PWA / Installable Website Support

Included:
- favicon
- app icons
- manifest
- service worker

Purpose:
- Better branding
- installable web-app style support
- improved icon handling on desktop/mobile shortcuts


16. Motion / UI Experience

Public website includes:
- formal entrance animations
- soft section reveals
- premium hover polish
- hero motion
- stats number animation
- splash screen
- admin-controlled animation toggle
- admin-controlled dark mode toggle

Admin panel includes:
- matching dark mode support
- formal administrative wording
- live dashboard refresh for new admissions and messages

Design goal:
- smooth
- formal
- professional
- not flashy


17. File Structure Summary

Key Source Files:
- index.html
- app.py
- requirements.txt
- runtime.txt
- Procfile
- .gitignore
- .htaccess
- favicon.svg
- favicon.ico
- site.webmanifest
- service-worker.js
